# Long description to be shown for this add-on on add-on information from add-
# ons manager
#: buildVars.py:17
msgid ""
"Provides enhanced terminal accessibility for Windows Terminal and "
"PowerShell, enabling screen reader users to efficiently navigate and "
"interact with command-line interfaces. Inspired by TDSR (Terminal Data "
"Structure Reader) and incorporates functionality from both TDSR and Speakup."
" Advanced features inspired by community suggestions and discussions."
msgstr ""
"Proporciona una accesibilidad mejorada a Windows Terminal y PowerShell, lo "
"que permite a los usuarios de lectores de pantalla navegar e interactuar de "
"manera eficiente con las interfaces de línea de comandos. Inspirado en TDSR "
"(Terminal Data Structure Reader) e incorpora funcionalidades tanto de TDSR "
"como de Speakup. Funciones avanzadas inspiradas en las sugerencias y debates"
" de la comunidad."

#: buildVars.py:14
msgid "Terminal Access for NVDA"
msgstr "Acceso a la terminal para NVDA"
